'''Kyösti Kakkonen''' (born December 7, 1956 in [[Kiihtelysvaara]]) is a [[Finland|Finnish]] businessman, art collector and millionaire. He is the chief executive officer of [[Tokmanni]]. 

Kyösti also collects art.<ref>http://yle.fi/uutiset/kyosti_kakkosen_laaja_grafiikkakokoelma_emmaan/1717150 Yle.fi ''finnish''</ref>

